An Openserve fibre break in Centurion has been fixed, the company told MyBroadband. The line break, which occured inÂ Rooihuiskraal, resulted in users in the Centurion area being impacted. Several users in Midstream Estate told MyBroadband they have not had Openserve fibre connectivity since yesterday afternoon. Openserve told MyBroadband the break occurred at around 14:30 on 27 February, and was repaired just after 07:00 this morning. The cause of the break is yet to be determined.